review 1: I've got a fetish for good food and this place gets me hot! The experience was heavenly as I was served a meal fit for God himself. The decor was unique and incredible. The waitress did an excellent job. I was happy to see how clean everything was. Overall experience: 5 stars.
review 2:
I believe the warung is now called Win-win.

Really good food.  All pork dishes.  Had a sampling of each pork dish.  Very delicious. They do not speak much English but we still managed to communicate with the little Indonesian I knew and google translate helps too!

Totally recommend to anyone who wants to eat where the locals eat!
review 4: Very delicious foods in this food stall.
